sentences: Candice Rickelle Glover (born November 22, 1989) is an American R&B singer and actress who won the twelfth season of American Idol.
Her debut album Music Speaks was released on February 18, 2014.
Candice Rickelle Glover was born on November 22, 1989, in Beaufort, South Carolina, to John and Carole Glover.
